{"tid":195261,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人做工程／建築","createTime":"2017-04-10T13:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T03:32:08.000Z","uid":66055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc98d3859c7f73fde3b13fafc005c9222128fe69","tid":195261,"uid":66055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"老豆係大陸18線城市買左間屋<br />\n係咁讚大陸d樓起得好靚 裝修技術先進過香港好撚多 乜乜柒柒<br />\n有冇人知實情係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好<br />\n<br />\n同佢仲叫我返去嗰個18線城市搵工 <br />\n話大陸人工就黎高過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e717292f33ebbed8ae06e76ca987476331db2d71","tid":195261,"uid":80958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:15:50.000Z","msg":"起得靚 係你老豆自己覺得靚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做呢行既就可能未必咁睇。"},{"pid":"d25ca81f6c83a065de1b414753c3c9e2afec4ec6","tid":195261,"uid":66055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起得靚 係你老豆自己覺得靚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做呢行既就可能未必咁睇。</blockquote><br />\n佢係話技術先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以上黎連登問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日聽佢歌頌大陸真係好閪煩"},{"pid":"72ff16a46036bedcb454a0114aad88f24959fab2","tid":195261,"uid":68079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:26:58.000Z","msg":"D樓睇落就靚，用料呢？之前防火物料用發泡膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鋼筋都隨時少幾條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Lift 還神經，夾到人個feedback system 係detect/反應唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e5c661bd95aac09443588ef33245605f01d3bf","tid":195261,"uid":83016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:44:19.000Z","msg":"良心企業全世界都有<br />\n黑心企業都一樣<br />\n根本就同地區無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c13b16a57a4d10f01b6498060acf616bf0ee72","tid":195261,"uid":70291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:59:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>良心企業全世界都有<br />\n黑心企業都一樣<br />\n根本就同地區無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n良心企業係大陸好難生存，好似係"},{"pid":"5b16bedf6f48aa7642860b5f882544afcd81cbff","tid":195261,"uid":48605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>良心企業全世界都有<br />\n黑心企業都一樣<br />\n根本就同地區無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過大陸特別多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc37ecb3afca52665d62f79865b18508b6c864e","tid":195261,"uid":70551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆係大陸18線城市買左間屋<br />\n係咁讚大陸d樓起得好靚 裝修技術先進過香港好撚多 乜乜柒柒<br />\n有冇人知實情係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好<br />\n<br />\n同佢仲叫我返去嗰個18線城市搵工 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話大陸人工就黎高過香港</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n大城市物價就跟得上香港啦<br />\n人工既話無父幹無學歷我睇都幾難高過香港<br />\n就算係大陸返工 都會去d一線城市做高科技/專業工作 返得二三線城市又想搵大錢既多數自己開廠做生意 幫人打工就算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"a4e863892e684b0dd32c8784d71a1bcaaa0c8320","tid":195261,"uid":66877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"靚？你見到既係裝修姐，內籠石矢防水落石矢果陣做成點，已經比裝修覆蓋哂。<br />\n唔好話大陸，香港既都唔一定好，更何況係大陸唔知幾多線城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735d93cf833f0cb29c03ee622d10a248511dd65b","tid":195261,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆係大陸18線城市買左間屋<br />\n係咁讚大陸d樓起得好靚 裝修技術先進過香港好撚多 乜乜柒柒<br />\n有冇人知實情係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好<br />\n<br />\n同佢仲叫我返去嗰個18線城市搵工 <br />\n話大陸人工就黎高過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係先進過香港 好多人工智能 因為立法會啲人係咁拉布 唔通過啲先進技術 話浪費錢 又話等技術成熟左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}